<P><Q><L><HI>&mdash;Seu me tranquilla &s;enectus</HI></L>
<L><HI>Expectat, &s;eu Mors atris circumvolat alis,</HI></L>
<L><HI>Dives, inops, Romae, &s;eu fors ita ju&s;&s;erit, exul,</HI></L>
<L><HI>Qui&s;quis erit vitae, &s;cribam, color.&mdash;</HI></L>
<BIBL>HOR.</BIBL></Q>
