<Q><L>Whether Old Age a tranquil evening brings,</L>
<L>Or Death &s;ails round me with his Raven Wings;</L>
<L>Rich, poor; at Rome, or London; well, or ill;</L>
<L>Whate'er my fortunes, write I mu&s;t and will.</L></Q></P>
